trans-unit.source: Converts service, contract, and endpoint information into metadata documents.
trans-unit.target: Konverterar service, kontraktet och slutpunkten information till metadata dokument.

trans-unit.source: Use the WsdlExporter class to transform <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> objects into metadata represented by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects.
trans-unit.target: Använd klassen WsdlExporter för att omvandla <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>objekt till metadata som representeras av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>objekt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WsdlExporter is used in a three-step process.
trans-unit.target: WsdlExporter används i tre steg.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A> method, passing the appropriate parameters.
trans-unit.target: Anropa den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A>metod och skicka lämpliga parametrar.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Determine whether there are any export errors by checking the base <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollera om det finns några exportfel genom att kontrollera basen <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>

trans-unit.source: If there are no errors, use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects or get more specific versions of the metadata using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Om det inte finns några fel, Använd den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A>att hämta en uppsättning <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>objekt eller hämta mer specifika versioner av metadata med hjälp av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can support exporting custom WSDL extensions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> interface and custom policy assertions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> interface.
trans-unit.target: Du kan stödja export av anpassade WSDL-tillägg genom att implementera den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>gränssnitt och anpassade principkontroller genom att implementera den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>gränssnitt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: For details, see the documentation for those interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i dokumentationen för de gränssnitt.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `WsdlExporter` can only be used to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances that contain Common Language Runtime (CLR) type information, such as a `ContractDescription` instance created using the `ContractDescription.GetContract` method or created as part of the `ServiceDescription` for a `ServiceHost` instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den `WsdlExporter` kan bara användas för att exportera metadata från `ContractDescription` instanser som innehåller Runtime CLR (Common Language) Ange information, till exempel en `ContractDescription` instans som har skapats med hjälp av den `ContractDescription.GetContract` metod eller skapas som en del av den `ServiceDescription` för en `ServiceHost` instans.

trans-unit.source: You cannot use the `WsdlExporter` to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances imported from service metadata or constructed without type information.
trans-unit.target: Du kan inte använda den `WsdlExporter` att exportera metadata från `ContractDescription` instanser importeras från tjänstmetadata eller konstrueras utan typinformation.
